Doolarka Bariga Caribbean (calaamad: $; code: XCD) waa lacagta dhammaan toddoba xubnood oo buuxa iyo hal xubin oo ka tirsan Ururka Dawladaha Bariga Caribbean (OECS). Hantidhawrka Ingiriisiga Galbeedka Hindiya, waxa uu jiray ilaa 1965, waxaana caadi ahaan loo soo gaabiyey Doolarka Dollar $ ama, haddii kale, EC $ si loo kala sooco lacagaha kale ee doolarka doolarka. EC $ waxaa loo qaybiyaa 100 senti. Lacagta Mareykanka ah ayaa loo qoondeeyey dollar tan iyo 7dii July 1976, sicirka sarrifku waa US $ 1 = EC $ 2.70. [1]
